Setup:
------

npm init
npm install puppeteer mocha chai 


.prettierrc:

{
  "semi": false,
  "singleQuote": true,
  "useTabs": true,
  "tabWidth": 2,
  "bracketSpacing": true,
  "arrowParens": "avoid",
  "trailingComma": "es5"
}


Advantages:
------------
- Developed by Google chrome team
- Modern javascript syntax
- zero config
- Fast & Stable
- No selenium
- uses dev tools protocol


CI setup:
---------

java -jar jenkins.war -httpPort=8080 --enable-future-java
npm run smoke-test


